message:
Evening,

Tomorrow myself and Michael Francis will be meeting for project abide at the Purple Onion from 8-10/11
I would love love LOVE to see some of y'all come out to study God's word and witness to the people around you. (Check 1 Timothy 4:11-13, good stuff there)

Cool thing though:
If you were @ Shift last night you heard about the organic prayer gatherings that were happening
If you want your Friday soaked in Jesus, come earlier and join me in prayer @ 7:30 am for our campus and whatever/whoever else may be on your mind and stick around for a quiet time! 

Reach out to me with any questions
Peace n' blessings.
Emily - out.
